00:15:26.533 --> 00:15:27.572
Salamat, Guro.

00:15:45.352 --> 00:15:46.932
Hindi nagpakita ang paring Daoist na ito

00:15:47.092 --> 00:15:48.253
anumang palatandaan ng banal na kapangyarihan.

00:15:48.852 --> 00:15:50.092
Eksakto.

