Ang musikang pinapatugtog mo

00:17:07.973 --> 00:17:09.172
ay walang kapantay.

00:17:10.293 --> 00:17:12.693
Maging ang mahistrado
ay nakiusap ng tatlong buwan

00:17:13.172 --> 00:17:14.372
at hindi pa rin kita nakilala.

00:17:15.493 --> 00:17:16.852
natural,

00:17:18.172 --> 00:17:19.652
nahihigitan mo ang mahistrado.

00:17:26.453 --> 00:17:28.933
