00:17:28.933 --> 00:17:32.904
♪Paano ako nagkasala♪

00:17:35.852 --> 00:17:38.693
♪Sa anong krimen ako sinisisi♪

00:17:38.693 --> 00:17:42.824
♪Labis ang pagdadalamhati ng puso ko♪

00:17:46.493 --> 00:17:49.652
♪Hindi kabilang sa panlabas♪

00:17:49.652 --> 00:17:53.253
♪Hindi umaalis sa loob♪

00:17:55.412 --> 00:17:57.933
♪Inilabas ako ng langit♪

00:17:57.933 --> 00:18:03.013
♪Nasaan ang aking nakatakdang oras♪

